<td>–</td>
<td>–</td>
<td>–</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th>ư</th>
<td><i>ưi</i> <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[ɨɪ̯]</span></td>
