<td><i>ay</i> <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[aɪ̯]</span></td>
<td><i>au</i> <span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">[aʊ̯]</span></td>
<td>–</td>
<td>–</td>
<td>–</td>
</tr>
<tr>
